==English==
===Alternative spellings===
*[[tres chic]]
*[[tre chic]] (common misspelling)

===Etymology===
From [[French]]. Literally "very [[chic]]". An extra "très" can be added to add more emphasis to the statement.

===Phrase===
'''[[très]] [[chic]]'''
#An [[expression]] that something is in [[style]] and/or [[desirable]].

